  "description": {
    "zh": "来，拿着这个——一把短款 AKS-74，也就是“AKS-74U”。你们这些专业的和街头混混都挺爱用这种枪的，毕竟轻便、短小、便宜，还能用 AK-74 的弹。\n\n我猜你之前干掉的那些人里有不少都拿过这玩意儿。\n\n现在你得去海关区域测试一下，帮我一个客户搜集点数据。他特别想知道这款枪在那种环境下的具体表现，尤其是在装了 Zenit DTK-1 补偿器的配置下。\n\n听说以前有人在战斗中用它表现很差，不如你来打个样？",
    "en": "Here take this - A short AKS-74, the \"AKS-74U\". You operators and bandits seem to love these weapons, after all they are compact, light, very cheap and uses the same caliber as the full size AK-74s.\n\nI assume you saw these weapons before, on the bandits or whoever else you killed.\nYou will need to test it in the Customs zone for a client of mine, he wants some statistics on it's performance in these kind of areas, and in specific configurations. You need to use the weapon attached with a Zenit muzzle brake, a DTK-1.\n\nPeople who had to use this in combat weren't so excited about it's performance, maybe you can prove them wrong?"
  },
